title: The rainy day sessions Vol.1-8
description:
The rainy day sessions


In 2010 in a thread on /v/, vidya game music was put together with rainymood.com

Someone madewith suggestions from that thread and his own recommendations but it wasn't updated since, now all download links there are dead.

These are the albums from that blog, untouched versions and also spliced with the sound of rain from rainymood.
